    "content": "Stomp - The Brothers Johnson\r\nTuning: EADG\r\n\r\nThis song is really funky brothers johnson and is really fun to play on bass. I'm not \r\nsure what he plays in the bass solo but i still tabbed something thats pretty close like it.\r\n\r\nThe order goes like this....\r\n\r\n[Intro]\r\n[Pre-Verse] x2\r\n[Verse] x4\r\n[Bridge]\r\n[Chorus]\r\n[Pre Verse] x2\r\n[Verse] x4\r\n[Bridge]\r\n[Chorus] x2\r\n[Slap solo]\r\n[Guitar Solo]\r\n[Chorus]\r\n[Chorus] (let ring at end note)\r\n[Chorus] x2\r\n[Chorus] (let ring at end note)\r\n[Outro]\r\n\r\nENJOY!\r\n\r\n[Intro]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-5------3--------|-----------------|-----------------|--------3-3-5----|\r\nA|----------6------|------5--3-------|------5--6-------|-----------------|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-5------3--------|-----------------|-----------------|--------3-3-5----|\r\nA|----------6------|------5--3-------|------5--6-------|-----------------|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-5---5-3---------|-----------------|-----------------|-------3-3-5---5-|\r\nA|---------6-6-6---|---6-5-3-3-3-----|---3-5-6-6-6-----|----6------------|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-5---5-3---------|-----------------|-----------------|-------3-3-------|\r\nA|---------6-6-6---|---6-5-3-3-3-----|---3-5-6-6-6-----|-----------3-----|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Pre-Verse:]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------33-----|------------53---|\r\nD|---3-5-----------|-----3-5---------|\r\nA|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nE|-3-----3--------0|1/3-------3------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------33-----|------------53---|\r\nD|---3-5-----------|-----3-5---------|\r\nA|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nE|-3-----3--------0|1/3-------3------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Bridge]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|--2--------------|-----------------|----0h1---2------|-----------------|\r\nA|-----0-2---------|--0--3-0-5-------|0h1---------0-2--|-0h2----3-0-5----|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|---7---7---7---7-|---8---8---8--8--|\r\nD|----0h1---2------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nA|0h1----------02--|0--3-0-2----034--|-5---5---5---5---|-6---6---6---6---|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-5-3-5-3---------|-----------------|-----------------|----------3-3-5-3|\r\nA|----------6-6----|-5-6-5-6-5---3-3-|-1-3-5---6-6-----|-5-6-5-6---------|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nD|-5-3-5-3---------|-----------------|-----------------|----------3------|\r\nA|----------6-6----|-5-6-5-6-5---3-3-|-1-3-5---6-6-----|-5-6-5-6----3----|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Slap Bass Solo:]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--0--0--0--3----|--0--0--0-3------|--0--0--0--5-----|--0---0----5----3|\r\nD|------------3h5-|--------------3h5|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nA|----------------|-----------3h5---|-------------3h5-|----------3---1--|\r\nE|3x-3--3---------|3x-3--3----------|3x-3--3----------|3x--3------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--0--0--0--3----|--0--0--0-3------|--0--0--0--5-----|--0---0---0---0--|\r\nD|------------3h5-|--------------3h5|-----------------|-----------------|\r\nA|----------------|-----------3h5---|-------------3h5-|-----------------|\r\nE|3x-3--3---------|3x-3--3----------|3x-3--3----------|3x--3---3---3----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Guitar Solo:]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----5---3-x3-3h5-|----5---3-x3-3h5-|---5--3-x3-3h5-|----5--3-x3--3h5-|\r\nD|-----------------|-----------------|---------------|-----------------|\r\nA|-33---3---------0|-33---3---------0|-33--3--------0|-33--3----------0|\r\nE|-----------------|-----------------|---------------|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Outro]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------/17-15--|----------------|---------/17-15--|-----------------|\r\nD|---------------17|-53-----------5-|-3-34----------17|-53------------5-|\r\nA|-----------------|---5------------|-----------------|---5-------------|\r\nE|-----------------|----3------033-0|-----------------|----3-------033-0|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------/17-15--|\r\nD|-3-34----------17|\r\nA|-----------------|\r\nE|-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nAfter a while the the outro riff starts to fade out.\r\n\r\nSo there you are. If you have any troubles or would like to suggest something just email me.\r\n\r\nadrian_acmilan_@hotmail.com\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n************************************\r\n\r\n| /  Slide up\r\n| h  Hammer-on\r\n| x  Dead note\r\n\r\n************************************",
